<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="14100000t" end="40800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">各位的罪行根本无关紧要</p>
<p begin="40800000t" end="49200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">好了</p>
<p begin="49200000t" end="78400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">请问音无董事长是怎么杀死澄女士的呢</p>
<p begin="87500000t" end="101300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">这个问题是有答案的</p>
<p begin="116300000t" end="131700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">请各位仔细思考</p>
<p begin="213100000t" end="236400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">在四季中转瞬即逝之冬</p>
<p begin="236400000t" end="264800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">有位如雪般的美人</p>
<p begin="264800000t" end="287300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">折羽织缎只为祈愿</p>
<p begin="287300000t" end="315700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">落下泪珠化身为鹤</p>
<p begin="315700000t" end="338200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">踏上寻找世界尽头旅途</p>
<p begin="338200000t" end="366600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">沙漠中的少年</p>
<p begin="366600000t" end="389100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">释放了神灯的精灵</p>
<p begin="389100000t" end="417500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">获得无可取代的财富</p>
<p begin="417500000t" end="469600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">精巧隐瞒的真象 形同幻化</p>
<p begin="469600000t" end="503800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">之中能有什么意义?</p>
<p begin="503800000t" end="543400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">人生! 一切! 皆是! 神秘!</p>
<p begin="558800000t" end="603100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">让我们背对太阳</p>
<p begin="603100000t" end="656800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">轻轻为无形的未来染上色彩</p>
<p begin="656800000t" end="705200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">来杯刚泡好热腾腾的红茶吧</p>
<p begin="705200000t" end="734000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">宴会已经开始了</p>
<p begin="734000000t" end="768200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">快告诉我 夜色中的故事</p>
<p begin="833700000t" end="854100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">我先去外面一下</p>
<p begin="865400000t" end="900400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">我该通知薰子这个状况</p>
<p begin="924200000t" end="952600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">我也去外面喘口气</p>
<p begin="1260000000t" end="1278700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">是不是精神疲劳了啊?</p>
<p begin="1278700000t" end="1301200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">不然我们也回房吧</p>
<p begin="1301200000t" end="1314200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">不, 不用了</p>
<p begin="1314200000t" end="1343400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">谁知道回房后你会做出什么事</p>
<p begin="1343400000t" end="1365100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">反正晚上还是要一起睡的啊</p>
<p begin="1365100000t" end="1400500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">九郎学长, 这打扮很适合你呢</p>
<p begin="1400500000t" end="1423000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">把这当成睡衣如何</p>
<p begin="1423000000t" end="1438900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">会很难睡吧</p>
<p begin="1448900000t" end="1466800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">音无董事长当时…</p>
<p begin="1466800000t" end="1506500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">知道大家各自计划过杀人吗</p>
<p begin="1506500000t" end="1544800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">不, 只是我靠个人情报和推测</p>
<p begin="1544800000t" end="1568600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">顺利套出他们的话而已</p>
<p begin="1568600000t" end="1603200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">对董事长来说是万万没想到的事实</p>
<p begin="1603200000t" end="1636200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">那其实没有必要揭穿吧</p>
<p begin="1636200000t" end="1669500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">音无董事长要是知道会很惊讶吧</p>
<p begin="1669500000t" end="1689100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">谁叫他要指派那么奇妙的课题</p>
<p begin="1689100000t" end="1712500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">发生怪事也没什么好意外的</p>
<p begin="1712500000t" end="1749200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">这部分我就趁今天跟他说吧</p>
<p begin="1749200000t" end="1772500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">还有, 我刚才也说了</p>
<p begin="1772500000t" end="1810900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">不先揭穿这些的话, 大家根本无法专心</p>
<p begin="1810900000t" end="1868100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">这么做也比较容易引导他们</p>
<p begin="1868100000t" end="1911400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">你不等他们想出自己的答案吗</p>
<p begin="1911400000t" end="1930600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">这么做比较轻松啊</p>
<p begin="1930600000t" end="1974800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">我已经给出许多能让他们</p>
<p begin="1974800000t" end="2020300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">只要再稍微暗示被害者的为人</p>
<p begin="2020300000t" end="2053700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">就算不那么做, 他们或许也会自己察觉</p>
<p begin="2053700000t" end="2082900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">最有希望的应该是莉音小姐</p>
<p begin="2089100000t" end="2135000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">她的话或许今晚就能找到我期待的答案</p>
<p begin="2145000000t" end="2181700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">虽然我早有觉悟和晋的罪行会曝光</p>
<p begin="2181700000t" end="2199200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">想不到事情不只这样…</p>
<p begin="2203800000t" end="2232200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">我很惊讶薰子和耕也竟然也这么打算</p>
<p begin="2232200000t" end="2247600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">既然有想到会这样</p>
<p begin="2247600000t" end="2266800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">爸爸你自己来不就好了</p>
<p begin="2266800000t" end="2279700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">抱歉</p>
<p begin="2289700000t" end="2309300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">我也曾经犹豫过</p>
<p begin="2309300000t" end="2341500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">我本来认为这段过往只能隐瞒一辈子</p>
<p begin="2341500000t" end="2362700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">但又觉得让你或爸爸知道</p>
<p begin="2362700000t" end="2382300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">能让我轻松一些</p>
<p begin="2382300000t" end="2406100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">所以觉得无论是你发现真相</p>
<p begin="2406100000t" end="2434000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">还是爸爸来告发我都好</p>
<p begin="2434000000t" end="2462000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">我就是不想自己说出口</p>
<p begin="2479900000t" end="2520800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">晋叔叔也像是被岩永琴子逼迫才自白的</p>
<p begin="2520800000t" end="2535000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">所以我懂你的心情</p>
<p begin="2535000000t" end="2549200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">我没有要生气</p>
<p begin="2549200000t" end="2578800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">知道自己的父亲想杀害祖母</p>
<p begin="2578800000t" end="2604590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">你还真是冷静呢</p>
<p begin="2617600000t" end="2669700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">我果然还是无法好好想象祖母是怎样的人</p>
<p begin="2669700000t" end="2700100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">所以该说没什么实感吗…</p>
<p begin="2700100000t" end="2740200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">我有听说她是把音无集团</p>
<p begin="2746000000t" end="2799400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">但同时也是被家人憎恨到</p>
<p begin="2799400000t" end="2815700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">可是不知道为什么…</p>
<p begin="2815700000t" end="2831900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">爸爸, 晋叔叔</p>
<p begin="2831900000t" end="2852800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">耕也姑丈和祖父提到祖母时</p>
<p begin="2852800000t" end="2888700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">我都感觉不到你们对她有恨意</p>
<p begin="2888700000t" end="2909500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">明明大家都恨到想杀她</p>
<p begin="2909500000t" end="2930400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">却让人觉得负面情感很薄弱…</p>
<p begin="2930400000t" end="2964200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">所以那段过去也让我觉得不太真实</p>
<p begin="2964200000t" end="3001300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">这个嘛, 我当时的确相当恨她</p>
<p begin="3008000000t" end="3036700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">只要她还在, 一切都会化为乌有</p>
<p begin="3049200000t" end="3066800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">大家都那么说</p>
<p begin="3066800000t" end="3111800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">但在她死后很久我才开始明白</p>
<p begin="3111800000t" end="3144300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">她并非不听旁人意见的暴君</p>
<p begin="3144300000t" end="3173500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">也不是没有考虑我们的幸福</p>
<p begin="3179400000t" end="3200200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">她也是个牺牲者</p>
<p begin="3200200000t" end="3254000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">她只是深信自己收到的命令并照着做而已</p>
<p begin="3254000000t" end="3282400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">命令? 谁的命令?</p>
<p begin="3282400000t" end="3315300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">就是她的父亲传次郎</p>
<p begin="3333300000t" end="3362500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">把音无集团做大的虽然是妈妈</p>
<p begin="3362500000t" end="3390000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">但那是传次郎命令她这么做的</p>
<p begin="3395800000t" end="3426700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">他在生前就订好详细的计画与方针</p>
<p begin="3426700000t" end="3442500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">并托付给自己的女儿</p>
<p begin="3449200000t" end="3490900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">音无澄这个人只不过是遵照指示前进罢了</p>
<p begin="3497600000t" end="3519700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">妈妈和你祖父刚一的婚姻</p>
<p begin="3519700000t" end="3553500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">也是传次郎无视妈妈意愿决定的</p>
<p begin="3553500000t" end="3584400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">为了集团要生几个孩子</p>
<p begin="3584400000t" end="3610200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">用什么方式让孩子们继承集团</p>
<p begin="3610200000t" end="3634800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">帮孩子挑选什么结婚对象</p>
<p begin="3634800000t" end="3669000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">妈妈全都是照着传次郎的决定走的</p>
<p begin="3674400000t" end="3713700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">传次郎所规划的蓝图就是如此具体</p>
<p begin="3713700000t" end="3754500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">所以我被要求以长男的身分继承集团</p>
<p begin="3754500000t" end="3783700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">晋被命令要贯彻辅佐我的职责</p>
<p begin="3783700000t" end="3822900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">薰子则得和家世显赫的男性结婚</p>
<p begin="3822900000t" end="3845000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">所以逼迫她跟耕也分手</p>
<p begin="3845000000t" end="3884700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">她认为那对我们来说是最幸福</p>
<p begin="3884700000t" end="3910500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">也是对集团最有利的决定</p>
<p begin="3925500000t" end="3944700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">而最可怕的点在于…</p>
<p begin="3944700000t" end="3958900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">当她还在世的时候</p>
<p begin="3958900000t" end="3982300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">一切都非常顺利</p>
<p begin="3991000000t" end="4032700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">那时集团按照传次郎生前规划的蓝图</p>
<p begin="4032700000t" end="4050700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">顺利地发展</p>
<p begin="4050700000t" end="4075300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">传次郎选择的丈夫非常优秀</p>
<p begin="4075300000t" end="4104100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">完美实现作为她左右手的职责</p>
<p begin="4104100000t" end="4122400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">我, 晋和薰子</p>
<p begin="4122400000t" end="4153700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">也都被养育成令她满意的孩子</p>
<p begin="4153700000t" end="4184100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">她遵从传次郎的吩咐, 排除反对者</p>
<p begin="4184100000t" end="4210800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">持续获得超过半个世纪的成功</p>
<p begin="4210800000t" end="4248800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">你觉得这样的人有办法突然违背命令吗</p>
<p begin="4248800000t" end="4286700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">有可能自己判断做错了就此收手吗</p>
<p begin="4293800000t" end="4338900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">而且是在还没碰上</p>
<p begin="4361000000t" end="4396400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">那…应该需要很大的勇气吧</p>
<p begin="4396400000t" end="4430200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">因为那等于是颠覆自己至今为止的价值观</p>
<p begin="4430200000t" end="4441500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">是啊</p>
<p begin="4441500000t" end="4473600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">她当时可以说是传次郎的傀儡</p>
<p begin="4473600000t" end="4505700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">我认为她其实有察觉到集团的危机</p>
<p begin="4505700000t" end="4543200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">也明白孩子们都有属于自己的幸福</p>
<p begin="4543200000t" end="4575800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">但认同这些事并改变方针</p>
<p begin="4575800000t" end="4593700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">就等于是要违抗传次郎</p>
<p begin="4593700000t" end="4623300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">舍弃至今的成功法则</p>
<p begin="4623300000t" end="4642100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">可是一直以来都很成功</p>
<p begin="4642100000t" end="4659200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">所以她无法舍弃原本的做法</p>
<p begin="4659200000t" end="4682100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">没错, 所以那个人…</p>
<p begin="4682100000t" end="4710900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">妈妈过世的时机真的非常刚好</p>
<p begin="4710900000t" end="4732600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">在那个时间点过世</p>
<p begin="4732600000t" end="4754300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">就不必亲眼见证集团因为自己崩溃</p>
<p begin="4754300000t" end="4782200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">也不必看孩子们落入不幸的样子</p>
<p begin="4782200000t" end="4841900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">至少不用面对被自己坚信的事物彻底背叛</p>
<p begin="4841900000t" end="4864800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">可以说她幸运也不为过</p>
<p begin="4879000000t" end="4892300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">就算如此我也不会</p>
<p begin="4892300000t" end="4924900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">为自己曾经想杀她的事辩解</p>
<p begin="4924900000t" end="4957800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">我的计画纯粹是为了自己的未来</p>
<p begin="4957800000t" end="4993300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">但是你一个人没办法执行计画对吧</p>
<p begin="4993300000t" end="5022500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">竟然寻求晋叔叔协助…</p>
<p begin="5022500000t" end="5066300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">我只要专注于一件事情上就会顾不得周遭</p>
<p begin="5066300000t" end="5096700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">而晋总是能冷静综观大局</p>
<p begin="5096700000t" end="5122200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">所以我最信任他的眼光</p>
<p begin="5122200000t" end="5146690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">我并不适合经营集团</p>
<p begin="5152200000t" end="5171790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">如果当时真的由我继承</p>
<p begin="5171790000t" end="5192600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">一切肯定会变得很糟糕</p>
<p begin="5192600000t" end="5225590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">这些话你直接告诉晋叔叔啦</p>
<p begin="5225590000t" end="5261900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">我讲过很多次了, 但他都不相信</p>
<p begin="5261900000t" end="5278100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">或许就是这样</p>
<p begin="5278100000t" end="5321900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">爸爸你们才能反抗家族的支配吧</p>
<p begin="5321900000t" end="5364000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">因为在祖母决定的环境中无法感到满足</p>
<p begin="5364000000t" end="5397800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">才会想走自己的道路</p>
<p begin="5397800000t" end="5427000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">是啊, 如果那时遵从她的命令</p>
<p begin="5427000000t" end="5446200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">觉得自己过得一帆风顺的话</p>
<p begin="5446200000t" end="5487500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">或许我们也会变成传次郎的傀儡</p>
<p begin="5497900000t" end="5538000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">成功体验有时会害到人, 甚至使人自灭</p>
<p begin="5543800000t" end="5585100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">她是不是一直都在给我们提示呢</p>
<p begin="5585100000t" end="5613900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">大家都有不在场证明和杀人计画</p>
<p begin="5613900000t" end="5646800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">如果是谋杀的话不会让被害者喊叫</p>
<p begin="5646800000t" end="5668100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">各自产生的矛盾</p>
<p begin="5668100000t" end="5698100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">却正是让人摆脱嫌疑的关键</p>
<p begin="5711100000t" end="5727700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">但是按照这个假说的话…</p>
<p begin="5734800000t" end="5757400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">爸爸, 你刚刚有说过</p>
<p begin="5757400000t" end="5784100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">祖母过世的时机非常刚好对不对</p>
<p begin="5784100000t" end="5805800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">我是有说, 怎么了?</p>
<p begin="5805800000t" end="5843300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">我或许知道事件的真相了</p>
<p begin="5962200000t" end="6011400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">我认为我知道23年前杀人事件的真相了</p>
<p begin="6018500000t" end="6045600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">我对终于得出的答案并不感到兴奋</p>
<p begin="6056800000t" end="6073500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">因为这只是岩永琴子打从一开始</p>
<p begin="6073500000t" end="6103100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">就试图引导我们找到的答案</p>
<p begin="6166900000t" end="6210300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">(被邀请来的裁判)</p>
<p begin="6214100000t" end="6235800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">祖母是自杀的</p>
<p begin="6235800000t" end="6253300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">所以才会包括祖父在内</p>
<p begin="6253300000t" end="6270400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">大家都有不在场证明</p>
<p begin="6296600000t" end="6307100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">莉音</p>
<p begin="6307100000t" end="6341700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">妈妈是个跟自杀完全扯不上边的人</p>
<p begin="6341700000t" end="6371300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">她可是会随心所欲控制周遭的人</p>
<p begin="6371300000t" end="6391700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">根本没有动机自杀</p>
<p begin="6391700000t" end="6423500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">但当时可以预见集团的崩坏了对吧</p>
<p begin="6423500000t" end="6466000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">所以大家才会计划谋杀祖母的不是吗</p>
<p begin="6466000000t" end="6497700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">而且晋叔叔和耕也姑丈</p>
<p begin="6497700000t" end="6526100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">应该也都注意到祖母被至今的成功所逼迫</p>
<p begin="6526100000t" end="6561100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">已经无法自己踩刹车了对吧?</p>
<p begin="6561500000t" end="6581900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">我们年纪也都大了</p>
<p begin="6581900000t" end="6608600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">当然能用不同观点看待当时的状况</p>
<p begin="6608600000t" end="6627400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">所以现在不会对她怀恨在心</p>
<p begin="6627400000t" end="6654100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">也明白妈妈其实是牺牲者</p>
<p begin="6654100000t" end="6685000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">祖母有很充足的动机自杀</p>
<p begin="6690000000t" end="6713300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">她是个优秀的经营者</p>
<p begin="6713300000t" end="6743800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">应该明白继续遵守传次郎的命令</p>
<p begin="6743800000t" end="6769200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">只会使集团崩溃</p>
<p begin="6777100000t" end="6813800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">集团崩溃等于违背传次郎的命令</p>
<p begin="6813800000t" end="6831300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">无论如何都得避免</p>
<p begin="6838400000t" end="6877200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">但不遵守命令也是背叛传次郎的行为</p>
<p begin="6888500000t" end="6923500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">这对祖母来说是非常可怕的事</p>
<p begin="6928900000t" end="6959000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">至今遵守命令持续获得的成功</p>
<p begin="6959000000t" end="6983600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">使她心理上无法挣脱这个束缚</p>
<p begin="6983600000t" end="7026500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">解决这矛盾情况的方法就是自杀</p>
<p begin="7031500000t" end="7049100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">那是让她能保护音无集团</p>
<p begin="7049100000t" end="7087000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">又不必感到恐惧的唯一手段</p>
<p begin="7112500000t" end="7149600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">但我实在不认为妈妈会自杀…</p>
<p begin="7149600000t" end="7175900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">我那时的确认为只要妈妈消失</p>
<p begin="7175900000t" end="7204200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">就能解决所有问题</p>
<p begin="7204200000t" end="7222200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">实际上一切也相当顺利</p>
<p begin="7228000000t" end="7254300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">妈妈本人若有这种自觉</p>
<p begin="7254300000t" end="7273000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">或许是会决定自杀</p>
<p begin="7273000000t" end="7288500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">但与其选择死亡</p>
<p begin="7288500000t" end="7330200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">违背传次郎的命令不是比较简单吗</p>
<p begin="7330200000t" end="7341000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">人在被逼迫时</p>
<p begin="7341000000t" end="7367700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">选择眼前的逃避手段也是很常见的事</p>
<p begin="7367700000t" end="7382300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">举例来说</p>
<p begin="7382300000t" end="7413600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">很多人会在事后说早点辞职不就好了</p>
<p begin="7413600000t" end="7447400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">早点断绝人际关系不就好了之类的话</p>
<p begin="7447400000t" end="7464900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">但从当事者的角度来看</p>
<p begin="7464900000t" end="7503700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">(外界压力 心理压力 工作)</p>
<p begin="7503700000t" end="7516200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">(人际关系)</p>
<p begin="7516200000t" end="7519500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">所以就会觉得能逃避责任</p>
<p begin="7519500000t" end="7555400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">把将来全都抛开的自杀很有吸引力</p>
<p begin="7568800000t" end="7587100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">如果有人能分担责任</p>
<p begin="7587100000t" end="7620900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">还能商量之后的事</p>
<p begin="7620900000t" end="7649200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">但澄女士并没有这样的对象吧?</p>
<p begin="7660500000t" end="7676000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">在那时候过世</p>
<p begin="7676000000t" end="7701800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">对祖母来说有很多好处</p>
<p begin="7701800000t" end="7718100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">我爸爸也说了</p>
<p begin="7718100000t" end="7741400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">"妈妈过世的时机真的非常刚好"</p>
<p begin="7741400000t" end="7761900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">"可以说她幸运也不为过"</p>
<p begin="7769400000t" end="7804800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">那么我认为可以说</p>
<p begin="7804800000t" end="7834000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">但祖母无法用单纯的方式自杀</p>
<p begin="7834000000t" end="7860700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">大集团的社长一旦自杀</p>
<p begin="7860700000t" end="7877400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">就会成为集团的丑闻</p>
<p begin="7877400000t" end="7895800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">整体形象也会变差吧</p>
<p begin="7901200000t" end="7919500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">一心想守护集团的祖母</p>
<p begin="7919500000t" end="7945000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">不可能容许这种事发生</p>
<p begin="7945000000t" end="7982500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">所以必须设法让人无法察觉是自杀</p>
<p begin="7990400000t" end="8023800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">所以才会伪装成强盗杀人</p>
<p begin="8023800000t" end="8050100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">让人认为是他杀吗</p>
<p begin="8050100000t" end="8079700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">从按摩店的回程中只有自己一人</p>
<p begin="8079700000t" end="8116000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">在住宅区的路上也不用担心会被人看见</p>
<p begin="8123100000t" end="8156000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">祖母便在那时执行了计画</p>
<p begin="8174800000t" end="8191500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">为了让人认为强盗抢走包包</p>
<p begin="8191500000t" end="8226100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">只从钱包拿走现金就逃跑</p>
<p begin="8226100000t" end="8246900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">她事先把钱包抽空</p>
<p begin="8246900000t" end="8268200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">并把空钱包和包包丢在地上</p>
<p begin="8274500000t" end="8295700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">再握住自己偷偷带着的小刀</p>
<p begin="8304100000t" end="8338300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">可是刀柄上没验出指纹吧</p>
<p begin="8338300000t" end="8378300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">只要用衣摆盖住刀柄再握住</p>
<p begin="8378300000t" end="8404600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">就不会留下指纹</p>
<p begin="8404600000t" end="8443000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">然后祖母为了制造他杀的印象</p>
<p begin="8443000000t" end="8460900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">刻意在最后大声喊叫</p>
<p begin="8500900000t" end="8513000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">抢劫啊</p>
<p begin="8513000000t" end="8553100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">谁来抓住那个穿黑色外套的男人</p>
<p begin="8553100000t" end="8566000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">他往车站跑了</p>
<p begin="8566000000t" end="8605200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">这么一来就更没人会怀疑她是自杀的</p>
<p begin="8605200000t" end="8638200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">虽然这样基本上就能达到祖母的目的</p>
<p begin="8638200000t" end="8670700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">然而警方认为是他杀的话就会展开搜查</p>
<p begin="8708700000t" end="8742400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">如果这时集团关系者被冠上杀人的嫌疑</p>
<p begin="8742400000t" end="8769500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">依旧会影响到企业的形象</p>
<p begin="8769500000t" end="8809200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">所以祖母为了不让关系者被怀疑</p>
<p begin="8809200000t" end="8840900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">刻意挑选大家应该</p>
<p begin="8850400000t" end="8875100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">这样的确说得通</p>
<p begin="8875100000t" end="8895900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">但如果妈妈是自杀的</p>
<p begin="8895900000t" end="8931800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">爸爸又为什么要说自己是犯人呢</p>
<p begin="8931800000t" end="8989800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">我想祖父可能是有计画地诱导祖母自杀</p>
<p begin="8989800000t" end="9033100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">故意展示让她认为自杀是最佳选择的资讯</p>
<p begin="9033100000t" end="9077400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">并且确信让祖母决意自杀的关键</p>
<p begin="9077400000t" end="9124500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">就是自己最后给予的情报</p>
<p begin="9159900000t" end="9175400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">我懂了</p>
<p begin="9175400000t" end="9219600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">所有孩子都计划谋杀她的事实</p>
<p begin="9219600000t" end="9247500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">成为她自杀的最后一根稻草了吧</p>
<p begin="9252900000t" end="9292100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">如果她在预料自己是使集团崩溃的主因时</p>
<p begin="9292100000t" end="9320900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">又发现自己为了孩子们幸福所付出的</p>
<p begin="9320900000t" end="9350500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">全都适得其反的话</p>
<p begin="9350500000t" end="9373100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">确实足以使她立刻决定自杀</p>
<p begin="9381800000t" end="9425600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">毕竟是孩子们全对自己抱持杀意这种事情</p>
<p begin="9425600000t" end="9452700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">如果是祖父故意让她察觉这件事</p>
<p begin="9458100000t" end="9495300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">那么说祖父是杀死祖母的犯人也不为过</p>
<p begin="9501900000t" end="9521100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">换句话说我和哥哥</p>
<p begin="9521100000t" end="9539900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">还有薰子姐姐和耕也</p>
<p begin="9539900000t" end="9572000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">都是杀死妈妈的帮凶吗</p>
<p begin="9594500000t" end="9607500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">谁知道呢</p>
<p begin="9607500000t" end="9639200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">就算是董事长也不见得能察觉你们的企图</p>
<p begin="9639200000t" end="9694600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">毕竟各位肯定都是很谨慎地暗中进行计画</p>
<p begin="9694600000t" end="9720500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">或许他只是为了把澄女士逼到自杀</p>
<p begin="9720500000t" end="9783000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">才捏造了孩子们都想杀她的证据来骗她</p>
<p begin="9783000000t" end="9815600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">只是这个谎言刚好与真相一致</p>
<p begin="9815600000t" end="9832300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">这样想比较自然吧</p>
<p begin="9832300000t" end="9854400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">还是真温柔呢</p>
<p begin="9854400000t" end="9876900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">但是我们也有责任</p>
<p begin="9876900000t" end="9905700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">不该让爸爸一个人背负</p>
<p begin="9905700000t" end="9928200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">就跟岩永小姐说的一样</p>
<p begin="9928200000t" end="9956100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">就算祖父亲口说出这个真相</p>
<p begin="9956100000t" end="9973200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">我们可能也不会相信</p>
<p begin="9973200000t" end="9996600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">如果不是将祖父视为犯人</p>
<p begin="9996600000t" end="10033700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">知道大家都曾计划谋杀祖母</p>
<p begin="10033700000t" end="10072500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">并客观审视祖母当时立场的话</p>
<p begin="10072500000t" end="10093400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">实在无法相信这种事情</p>
<p begin="10101300000t" end="10122600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">是祖父拜托你</p>
<p begin="10122600000t" end="10157600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">引导我们找到这个真相的对吧</p>
<p begin="10157600000t" end="10194700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">其实音无董事长觉得没有这个必要呢</p>
<p begin="10200100000t" end="10239800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">那么两位赞成莉音小姐的答案吗</p>
<p begin="10239800000t" end="10262700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">没问题的话就把这个当作最终答案</p>
<p begin="10262700000t" end="10301090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">明天中午告诉音无董事长吧</p>
<p begin="10309400000t" end="10333190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">应该没有更好的答案了</p>
<p begin="10333190000t" end="10347800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">我也同意</p>
<p begin="10347800000t" end="10387400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">那么继承遗产的优先权要怎么办呢</p>
<p begin="10387400000t" end="10414500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">虽然想出这个答案的人是莉音小姐</p>
<p begin="10414500000t" end="10444100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">名次就照一开始说好的顺序可以吗</p>
<p begin="10444100000t" end="10470000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">我这个想过谋杀母亲的人</p>
<p begin="10470000000t" end="10507100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">现在哪有脸说想要优先权呢</p>
<p begin="10507100000t" end="10525000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">薰子应该也是吧</p>
<p begin="10525000000t" end="10561300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">如果她脸皮有厚到这样还想要优先权的话</p>
<p begin="10561300000t" end="10589300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">一开始就不会害怕这个课题了</p>
<p begin="10596800000t" end="10621800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">事到如今还需要什么优先权吗</p>
<p begin="10621800000t" end="10655600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">请祖父适当分配就好了</p>
<p begin="10655600000t" end="10680200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">那就跟董事长这么说吧</p>
<p begin="10691500000t" end="10703100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">莉音小姐</p>
<p begin="10703100000t" end="10745300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">明天你能自己告诉董事长这个答案吗</p>
<p begin="10745300000t" end="10774000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">也可以由我代为传达喔</p>
<p begin="10774000000t" end="10797400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">我会直接告诉他</p>
<p begin="10797400000t" end="10812000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">让你转达的话</p>
<p begin="10812000000t" end="10833300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">好像会被讲成很有恶意的样子</p>
<p begin="10839500000t" end="10863700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">莉音这名字真好听</p>
<p begin="10863700000t" end="10887900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">就像是松鼠加上狮子</p>
<p begin="10887900000t" end="10919200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">很符合你可爱又勇猛的感觉</p>
<p begin="10937100000t" end="10963400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">为什么要乱说那种奇怪的解释</p>
<p begin="10963400000t" end="10997600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">就只是把狮子的英文用罗马拼音发音而已</p>
<p begin="11005500000t" end="11037200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">因为哥哥从小就喜欢狮子</p>
<p begin="11037200000t" end="11066800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">如果生的是男孩, 他肯定会取名叫玲央</p>
<p begin="11073100000t" end="11104000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">你这么了解亮马先生</p>
<p begin="11104000000t" end="11132300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">何不趁这个机会和解呢</p>
<p begin="11149000000t" end="11163600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">我考虑一下</p>
<p begin="11174000000t" end="11201600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">在那之前得先去帮妈妈扫墓</p>
<p begin="11201600000t" end="11216600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">妈妈也是在用自己的方式</p>
<p begin="11216600000t" end="11240800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">设法保护她认为该守护的事物</p>
<p begin="11240800000t" end="11270800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">想到这点, 就觉得应该重新悼念她才行</p>
<p begin="11270800000t" end="11307500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">这也得快点告诉薰子呢</p>
<p begin="11316700000t" end="11329600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">不过是不是该等明天</p>
<p begin="11329600000t" end="11361300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">和董事长证实过后再说呢</p>
<p begin="11418400000t" end="11441000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">这就是我们的答案</p>
<p begin="11441000000t" end="11462200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">祖父, 您觉得如何呢</p>
<p begin="11522700000t" end="11558200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">我应该早点这么做的</p>
<p begin="11558200000t" end="11589900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">亮马, 晋, 薰子和耕也…</p>
<p begin="11589900000t" end="11634100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">看来我一直让你们背负了过度的罪恶感呢</p>
<p begin="11674100000t" end="11693700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">这个答案是对的</p>
<p begin="11700800000t" end="11758400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">不过我当时并不知道你们计划谋杀母亲</p>
<p begin="11758400000t" end="11775000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">这部分是巧合</p>
<p begin="11805900000t" end="11869700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">不过我很庆幸抢先你们一步</p>
<p begin="11869700000t" end="11922300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">至少避免了让你们亲手杀害母亲</p>
<p begin="11922300000t" end="11949800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">不, 就算如此我和哥哥</p>
<p begin="11949800000t" end="11987700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">以及薰子姐姐和耕也都还是有罪</p>
<p begin="11987700000t" end="12014500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">虽然我们并不会受到法律的制裁</p>
<p begin="12014500000t" end="12029900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">毕竟也没有证据</p>
<p begin="12029900000t" end="12062000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">而且妈妈应该也不会恨你吧</p>
<p begin="12062000000t" end="12097500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">那时候大家真的都别无选择</p>
<p begin="12097500000t" end="12132500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">任何人都可能有杀死他人的念头</p>
<p begin="12132500000t" end="12160400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">也可能会伸手拿起凶器吧</p>
<p begin="12160400000t" end="12190500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">然而有没有跨越最后那一道界线</p>
<p begin="12190500000t" end="12206300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">仍有很大的差别</p>
<p begin="12206300000t" end="12235100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">害死澄的罪由我来背</p>
<p begin="12235100000t" end="12272200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">你们只要好好看着我的死状就行了</p>
<p begin="12290600000t" end="12309300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">虽然一直瞒着大家</p>
<p begin="12309300000t" end="12343100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">但我的身体早已被恶性肿瘤侵蚀</p>
<p begin="12354400000t" end="12379800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">院方诊断最多再半年我就会连站都站不住</p>
<p begin="12379800000t" end="12426100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">在剧痛的折磨下悲惨死去</p>
<p begin="12434900000t" end="12477000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">这份病痛就是我杀死澄的代价</p>
<p begin="12503300000t" end="12537100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">我不会选择缓和痛苦的治疗或安乐死</p>
<p begin="12537100000t" end="12561700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">会让病痛折磨我直到最后一刻</p>
<p begin="12569600000t" end="12600900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">一旦杀人就必须遭受相对的报应</p>
<p begin="12600900000t" end="12627100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">就算杀人让一切圆满顺利</p>
<p begin="12627100000t" end="12647600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">还是逃不过报应的</p>
<p begin="12647600000t" end="12694700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">千万不能把犯罪带来的成功视为理所当然</p>
<p begin="12694700000t" end="12735200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">他们都说要放弃继承遗产的优先权呢</p>
<p begin="12735200000t" end="12768500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">虽然想出答案的最大功臣是莉音小姐</p>
<p begin="12768500000t" end="12802700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">但她认为遗产照您的意思分配就好</p>
<p begin="12826100000t" end="12848200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">真是寡欲呢</p>
<p begin="12848200000t" end="12873200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">不, 我认为这是很正常的判断</p>
<p begin="12882000000t" end="12907800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">最大的功臣应该是你吧</p>
<p begin="12907800000t" end="12940400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">琴子小姐, 找你来果然是对的</p>
<p begin="12940400000t" end="12953300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">谢谢你</p>
<p begin="13003800000t" end="13030500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">现在道谢还太早啰</p>
<p begin="13061300000t" end="13090500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">如果董事长是亲手杀死妻子的</p>
<p begin="13090500000t" end="13125100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">那从一开始就不需要我来多嘴</p>
<p begin="13133900000t" end="13166400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">但是您选了很特异的方法</p>
<p begin="13172300000t" end="13212300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">我认为您应该借此机会认知到那并不正确</p>
<p begin="13212300000t" end="13256100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">董事长您现在很庆幸选择了那种方法</p>
<p begin="13256100000t" end="13273200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">因为正如您本人所说</p>
<p begin="13273200000t" end="13305300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">这避免了让孩子们成为弑母凶手</p>
<p begin="13311600000t" end="13321200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">这样的话</p>
<p begin="13321200000t" end="13335800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">并不能说您对过往的成功</p>
<p begin="13335800000t" end="13365400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">对这个选择感到后悔吧</p>
<p begin="13376600000t" end="13387100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">莉音小姐</p>
<p begin="13394200000t" end="13425900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">你说音无澄女士是自杀的</p>
<p begin="13425900000t" end="13472600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">那么为什么当时她不选择假装成意外呢</p>
<p begin="13472600000t" end="13485100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">这…</p>
<p begin="13485100000t" end="13520500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">像是要捡东西不小心跑到马路上</p>
<p begin="13520500000t" end="13563500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">或是在车站的月台不慎落轨</p>
<p begin="13563500000t" end="13580200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">只要本人有心</p>
<p begin="13580200000t" end="13601000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">要假装成意外是很简单的</p>
<p begin="13601000000t" end="13631900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">表面上不会被怀疑是自杀的人</p>
<p begin="13631900000t" end="13664400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">就算死亡时状况有点不自然</p>
<p begin="13664400000t" end="13683600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">也会被当作意外处理吧</p>
<p begin="13683600000t" end="13701600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">琴, 琴子小姐</p>
<p begin="13701600000t" end="13734500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">那么一来警察便不会仔细搜查</p>
<p begin="13734500000t" end="13763300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">也不必在意关系者有没有不在场证明</p>
<p begin="13763300000t" end="13800800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">实际上薰子小姐差点就失去不在场证明</p>
<p begin="13800800000t" end="13813300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">若不是真的骨折了</p>
<p begin="13813300000t" end="13834200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">肯定会被当成嫌疑犯</p>
<p begin="13834200000t" end="13865500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">而且要是警方认真进行搜查</p>
<p begin="13865500000t" end="13889200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">伪装的手段也很有可能暴露</p>
<p begin="13895500000t" end="13919300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">伪装成他杀的风险很高吧</p>
<p begin="13925500000t" end="13957600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">也就是说这起事件并没有进行他杀的伪装</p>
<p begin="13966400000t" end="13989800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">音无澄女士并非自杀</p>
<p begin="13989800000t" end="14015200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">这确实是一起谋杀案</p>
<p begin="14015200000t" end="14047300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">那么我们就来指出真正的犯人吧</p>
<p begin="14070200000t" end="14100300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">(待续)</p>
<p begin="14242900000t" end="14267900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">如果仅仅是为了自己</p>
<p begin="14267900000t" end="14296300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">而感到无能为力的时候</p>
<p begin="14305100000t" end="14348000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">只要为了你对我绽放的笑容</p>
<p begin="14348000000t" end="14363500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">所有不可能都不复存在</p>
<p begin="14371400000t" end="14437700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">无论是早晨中午夜晚 我都在梦想着</p>
<p begin="14437700000t" end="14472300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">即使在扭曲的世界里 也一定不会动摇</p>
